data.mutation:
mutation CreateAddressChangeQuotes(
  $contractBundleId: ID!
  $type: AddressHomeType!
  $street: String!
  $zip: String!
  $livingSpace: Int!
  $numberCoInsured:Int!
  $ownership: AddressOwnership!
  $startDate: LocalDate!
  $isStudent: Boolean
  $ancillaryArea: Int
  $yearOfConstruction: Int
  $numberOfBathrooms: Int
  $isSubleted: Boolean
  $extraBuildings: [AddressHouseExtraBuilding!]
) {
  	createAddressChangeQuotes(
		input: {
			contractBundleId: $contractBundleId
      		type: $type
      		street: $street
      		zip: $zip
      		livingSpace: $livingSpace
     		numberCoInsured: $numberCoInsured
      		ownership: $ownership
      		startDate: $startDate
      		isYouth: false
  			isStudent: $isStudent
  			ancillaryArea: $ancillaryArea
			yearOfConstruction: $yearOfConstruction
			numberOfBathrooms: $numberOfBathrooms
			isSubleted: $isSubleted
  			extraBuildings: $extraBuildings
		}
	) {
	  ... on AddressChangeQuoteSuccess {
      	quoteIds
      }
   	  ... on AddressChangeQuoteFailure {
      	breachedUnderwritingGuidelines
      }
	}
}
